hadiths[25]{hadithnumber,text}:
1505,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! janwer (qehat saali ki bina par) halak ho gaey aur raastey khatm ho gaey, Allah Taala sey (barish ki) dua kijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dua farmaee to is Jumey sey agley Jumey tak (musalsal) barish hoti rahi. to (wohi) aadmi Rasulullah key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! (ziyada barish ki wajeh sey) ghar gir gaey aur raastey munqata' ho gaey aur janwer marney lagey hain. to aap ney dua farmaee : aey Allah ! pahadon ki chotiyon par, tilon par, wadiyon key nasheb (naalon) aur janglaat mein barish barsa. to badal Madina Munawra sey is tarah chhat gaey jis tarah darmiyan sey kapda phat jata hai."
1506,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) . ۔ . jinhein khuwab mein Azan sikhlai gaee thi. . ۔ bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) barish ki dua karney key liye eid-gaah ki taraf nikley. aap qibley ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur apni chadar ultaai aur do rakatein padhin.Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye ibne uena ki ghalati hai kyonkey jis Abdullah bin Zaid ko khuwab mein Azan dikhlai gaee thi wo Abdullah bin Zaid bin Abde-Rabba hain jab ke mazkura hadees bayan karney waley Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim Mazni hain.
1507,"Hazrat Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Kinaana (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey falan shakhs ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas bheja ke main un sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaze-istisqaa key barey mein poochhun to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) gidgidaatey huye, aajizi key sath saada kapdon mein (aaraaish (sajawat) aur zeenat key baghair) nikley. aap ney tumharey is khutbey ki tarah khutba nahin diya, phir do rakaat padhin."
1508,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze-istisqaa padhaai to aap par siyah ooni chadar thi.
1509,"Hazrat Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Kinaana (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaze istisqaa key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) saada kapdon mein, aajizi key sath, gidgidaatey huye nikley, phir aap member par bethey lekin tumharey khutbey ki tarah khutba nahin diya balke aap dua kartey rahey, gidgidaatey rahey aur Allah Taala ki buzurgi bayan kartey rahey, phir aap ney eidain ki namaz ki tarah do rakaat padhin."
1510,"Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem key chacha (Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke main bhi dua'aey istisqaa key liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaya tha. aap ney apni chadar ultaai aur logon ki taraf pusht kar li aur dua karney lagey, phir do rakatein padhain aur un mein buland aawaz sey qirat ki."
1511,Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem key chacha sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney barish ki dua farmaee aur do rakatein padhin aur apni chadar ultaai.
1512,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( Madina Munawra sey) bahar nikley aur barish ki dua ki aur jab (dua key liye) qibla rukh huye to aap ney apni chadar ultaai.
1513,"Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem key chacha sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dua'aey istisqaa mein dekha. aap ney qibley ki taraf munh farmaya, chadar ko ultaaya aur (dua key liye) apney haath uthaey."
1514,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kisi bhi dua mein itney buland haath nahin uthatey they jitney dua'aey istisqaa (baarish ki dua) mein. aap is mein haath itney buland uthatey ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aati.
1515,"Hazrat Aabi Al Laham (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aehjaar-azz-zait key maqam par barish ki dua kartey dekha. aap ney apney haath uthaey huye they aur dua farma rahey they."
1516,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik dafa hum Jumey key din masjid mein they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko khutba dey rahey they ke eik aadmi khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! raastey khatm ho gaey aur janwer halak honey lagey aur shehron mein qehat pad gaya. Allah Taala sey dua farmaiye, hamen barish ata farmaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chehra mubarak key barabar apney haath uthaey aur farmaya : (اللھم ! اسقنا),''aey Allah ! hum par barish nazil farma.'' Allah ki qism ! abhi Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member sey nahin utrey they ke hum par khub zor sey barish barasney lagi balke us din sey agley Jumey tak barish barasti rahi. to eik aadmi khada huwa. . ۔ main nahin janta ye wohi shakhs tha jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey barish ki dua karney ko kaha tha ya koi aur . ۔ . us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! pani ki ziyadti ki wajeh sey raastey kat gaey aur janwer marney lagey. Allah Taala sey dua farmaiye ke Allah Taala hum sey barish rok ley. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dua farmaaee : (اللھم ! حو الینا), ''aey Allah ! hamarey ird-gird barish farma,''hum par na farma balke pahadon aur janglaat par barish farma. Allah ki qism ! junhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye kalimaat kahe. badal chatney lagey yahan tak ke hamein eik tukda bhi nazar na aata tha."
1517,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (اللھم ! اسقنا),''aey Allah ! hamein barish ata farma.''"
1518,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Jumey key din khutba irshad farma rahey they ke log khadey ho kar buland aawaz sey kehney lagey : aey Allah key Nabi ! barish (lambey arsey sey) ruki hui hai aur janwer mar rahey hain. Allah Taala sey dua farmaiye ke barish nazil farmaey. aap ney farmaya : (اللھم ! اسقنا), (اللھم ! اسقنا), ''aey Allah ! hamein pani pila. aey Allah ! hamen pani pila.'' Allah ki qism ! hum aasman mein badal ka eik tukda bhi nahin dekhtey they, phir eik chhota sa badal paida huwa, phir us ney phailna shuru kiya, phir wo barasney laga aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) member sey utrey aur namaz padhaai. log (barish mein) gharon ko gaey. agley Jumey tak (musalsal) barish hoti rahi. to jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutbey key liye khadey huye to logon ney phir buland aawaz sey kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! ghar gir gaey aur raastey kat gaey. Allah Taala sey dua kijiye, Allah Taala barish rok ley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : aey Allah ! hamarey ird-gird barish farma, hum par na farma. badal Madina Munawra sey chhat gaey. Madiney key ird-gird barish hoti thi aur Madiney main eik qatra bhi nahin barasta tha. mainey Madina Munawra ko dekha, aisey lagta tha jaisey is par taaj ho."
1519,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil huwa jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey khutba dey rahey they. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney aa kar khada ho gaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! janwer mar gaey aur raastey khatm ho gaey, Allah Taala sey dua kijiye ke Allah Taala hum par barish barsaey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath uthaey, phir farmaya : aey Allah ! hum par barish barsa, aey Allah ! hum par barish barsa. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : Allah ki qism ! hum aasman mein badal kya badal ka tukda bhi na dekhtey they, isi ke sath hamarey aur sala pahad key darmiyan koi makaan ya ghar bhi haael (rukawat) na tha. achcha dhaal jitna chhota sa badal ka tukda (pahad key peechhey sey) zahir huwa, jab wo aasman key darmiyan mein (yani hamarey saron par) aaya to phel gaya aur barasney laga. Hazrat Anas bayan kartey hain : Allah ki qism ! phir hamney pura hafta (saat din) suraj nahin dekha, phir aainda Jumey usi darwazey sey eik aadmi dakhil huwa jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they. wo aap key samney aa kar khada ho gaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala aap par (be shumar ) rahmatein farmaey. (pani ki kasrat ki bina par) janwer marney lagey hain aur raastey bhi toot gaey hain. Allah Taala sey dua farmaiye ke hum sey barish rok ley. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath uthaey aur farmaya : aey Allah ! hamarey ird-gird barish barsa, hum par na barsa. aey Allah ! tilon par, toodon par, wadiyon key nasheb (dhalaan) aur janglaat mein barish barsa. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (ye kehna tha ke) barish fauran ruk gaee aur hum masjid sey nikley to dhoop mein chaltey they. Shareek (raawi) ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya ye pehla aadmi hi tha? unhoney farmaya : nahin."
1520,"Hazrat Ibaad bin Tameem ney apney chacha (Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu)) sey suna jo ke as-haabe-Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mein sey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din barish ki dua karney nikley. aap ney dua key waqt logon ki taraf peeth kar li (yani aap ka rukh mubarak qibley ki taraf tha). aur aap ney apni chadar bhi ultaai thi, phir (dua key baad) aap ney do rakatein padhin aur un dono mein qirat bhi ki."
1521,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) barish ki dua karney key liye (shehar sey) bahar nikley, phir aap ney qibla rukh ho kar (dua ki aur) do rakatein padhin."
1522,"Hazrat Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Kinaana (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey kisi Ameer (Haakim) ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas bheja ke main un sey dua'aey istisqaa (baarish ki dua) key barey mein poochhun. Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya : usey kon si chiz khud mujh sey sawal karney sey rokti hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aajizi ki haalat mein saada kapdey pehan kar khushu, khuzoo key sath gidgidaatey huye (Madina Munawra sey) bahar nikley aur eidain ki namaz ki tarah do rakatein padhin aur tumharey khutbey ki tarah khutba nahin diya."
1523,"Hazrat ibaad bin Tameem key chacha sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (Madina Munawra sey) bahar nikley, barish ki dua ki, phir do rakatein padhin aur un mein buland aawaz sey qirat ki."
1524,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab barish barasney lagti to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : aey Allah ! zor sey barsa aur isey mufeed barish bana.
1525,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney farmaya : jab bhi main apney bandon par koi nemat (maslan : barish) nazil farmata hun to un mein sey eik giroh uski wajeh sey kufr ka kaam karta hai. kehta hai : hum par falan sitarey ney barish barsai hai ya hum falan sitarey sey sairab huye."
1526,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur main eik dafa aam barish hui to aap ney farmaya : kya tum jantey nahin ke tumharey Rab taala ney raat kya kaha? Allah Taala ney farmaya : jab main apney bandon par koi nemat (khusoosan barish) nazil farmata hun to un mein sey kuchh log uskey sath kufr kartey hain. kehtey hain : hum par falan sitarey ki wajeh sey barish hui, albatta jo shakhs mujh par eman rakhta hai aur merey barish barsaney par meri tareef karta hai, wo haqiqat mein momin hai aur sitaron ka kafir hai (yani sitaron ki taqat aur ikhtiyar ka munkir hai) aur jis shakhs ney kaha : hamein falan sitarey sey barish hui. wo merey sath kufr karta hai aur sitaron par eman rakhta hai."
1527,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar Allah Taala paanch saal tak apney bandon sey barish rokey rakhey, phir bhejey, tab bhi kuchh log zarur kufr kerengey. wo kahengey : hamein mijdah sitarey sey barish mili hai."
1528,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik saal tak barish ruki rahi to eik musalman Juma Mubarak key din (khutbey key doran mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney aa khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! barish (saal bhar sey) ruki hui hai, zamin banjar ho gaee hai aur janwer mar rahey hain. raawi bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath uthaey jab ke hum aasman par badal ka eik tukda bhi nahin dekhtey they. aap ney apney dono haath is qadr uthaey ke mainey aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi. aap Allah sey barish ki dua karney lagey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke abhi hum Juma padh kar farigh na huye they (yani abhi Jumey mein masroof they, itni barish barsi) ke hum mein qarib ghar waley nojawan shakhs ko bhi fikr laahiq ho gaee ke ghar kaisey pahunchunga (door waley aur boodhon ki to baat hi kya)? phir pura hafta barish barasti rahi. jab aglaa Juma aaya to logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (kasrate barish ki bina par) ghar gir gaey aur qafiley ruk gaey. aap insan key jaldi uktaa janey par muskuraaey, phir haath utha kar farmaya : aey Allah hamarey ird-gird barish barsa, hum par na barsa, fauran badal Madiney sey chhat gaey."
1529,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein logon par eik saal tak qehat pad gaya. eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Juma Mubarak key din member par khutba irshad farma rahey they ke eik erabi (dehaati) uth khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! janwer marney lagey hain aur baal bachchey bhookey hain, Allah Taala sey hamarey liye barish ki dua kijiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney dono mubarak haath utha diye. hum aasman par badal ka eik tukda bhi nahin dekhtey they. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! abhi aap ney haath nichey na farmaai they ke pahadon jaisey badal uthey, phir abhi apney member sey nichey nahin utrey they ke mainey barish key qatrey aap ki daadhi mubarak par barastey dekhey. wo din, aglaa din, us sey aglaa din yahan tak ke agley Jumey tak barish barasti rahi, phir wohi erabi (dehati) ya koi aur utha aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! ab to imaraten dheh gaeen, (ghar gir padey) janwer doobney lagey, Allah Taala sey hamarey liye barish key band honey ki dua farmaeyn. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney phir apney dono haath mubarak utha liye aur farmaya : aey Allah hamarey ird-gird barish farma, hum par na barsa. aap jis taraf key badal ki taraf bhi daste mubarak sey ishara farmatey wo chhat jata, yahan tak ke Madina Munawra hoz ki tarah ho gaya. wadi (qanaa eik maah tak) behti rahi aur jo shakhs bhi kisi ilaqey sey aaya, us ney khub barish batlaai."
